desc: If you don't have a wall to mount your charging station against, Ladeeda® is an elegant charging station, which is easy to install and fits nicely next to your car. Compatible with the Tesla Wall Connector, EVbox Elvi, Powerdale Nexxtender, Smappee Home, Easee, Wallbox Pulsar & others
